.SH NAME
history \- Show this shell pane's bounded command history.
.SH SYNOPSIS
.nf
history
.fi
.SH DESCRIPTION
Prints the bounded command history owned by the current shell pane, including the current history invocation.
.SH EXAMPLES
.nf
$ history
.fi
.SH SEE ALSO
help(1), man(1)
